    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. Parghi,",
        "I am Utsav Patel, who sat next to you on a flight from Toronto to Calgary on May 15th. You gave me your business card after hearing about my passion to work in a restaurant. I am writing regarding my keen interest to work in one of your restaurants as a cook.",
        "You were kind enough to suggest me that I should contact you if I ever want to work in a restaurant. As I mentioned in our conversation, I am studying in a food technician course which will finish within a month.",
